<section class="dc-faq" id="faq">
  <div class="dc-faq__inner">

    <div class="dc-faq__header">
      <p class="dc-eyebrow">FAQ</p>
      <h2 class="dc-h2">Your Questions, Answered</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="dc-faq__item">
      <button class="dc-faq__question" aria-expanded="false">
        What are collagen peptides and how do they work?
        <span class="dc-faq__icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      </button>
      <div class="dc-faq__answer" role="region">
        <div class="dc-faq__answer-inner">
          Collagen is the most abundant structural protein in the human body — it forms the foundation of your skin, hair, and nails. As we age, our natural collagen production declines from our mid-twenties. Collagen peptides are hydrolyzed (broken down) collagen molecules that are smaller and more bioavailable, meaning your body can absorb and utilise them more efficiently. DermaCore delivers collagen peptides alongside biotin, vitamins, and zinc to support beauty from within.*
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="dc-faq__item">
      <button class="dc-faq__question" aria-expanded="false">
        How long until I see results?
        <span class="dc-faq__icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      </button>
      <div class="dc-faq__answer" role="region">
        <div class="dc-faq__answer-inner">
          Results vary by individual. Most customers report noticing changes in nail strength and hair texture within 2 to 4 weeks. Skin improvements — including hydration and texture — are most commonly reported from week 3 to 6. For best results, we recommend consistent daily use for a minimum of 60 days. Beauty from within is a long game, not an overnight fix.* Individual results may vary.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="dc-faq__item">
      <button class="dc-faq__question" aria-expanded="false">
        How many gummies do I take per day and when?
        <span class="dc-faq__icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      </button>
      <div class="dc-faq__answer" role="region">
        <div class="dc-faq__answer-inner">
          Take 2 DermaCore gummies daily. You can take them any time of day — morning, afternoon, or evening — with or without food. We find most customers prefer taking them in the morning as part of their beauty ritual, which helps with consistency. Do not exceed 2 gummies per day unless directed by a healthcare professional.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="dc-faq__item">
      <button class="dc-faq__question" aria-expanded="false">
        Can I take DermaCore alongside my existing skincare?
        <span class="dc-faq__icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      </button>
      <div class="dc-faq__answer" role="region">
        <div class="dc-faq__answer-inner">
          Yes. DermaCore is designed to complement, not replace, your existing skincare routine. Think of it as the inner layer that topical skincare cannot reach. Collagen peptides, biotin, and vitamins work at a cellular level to support the skin's foundational structure — which can enhance the results you're getting from serums, moisturisers, and other topical products.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="dc-faq__item">
      <button class="dc-faq__question" aria-expanded="false">
        Is DermaCore suitable for vegetarians or vegans?
        <span class="dc-faq__icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      </button>
      <div class="dc-faq__answer" role="region">
        <div class="dc-faq__answer-inner">
          DermaCore's collagen peptides are derived from bovine (cattle) sources. Gelatin is also used in the gummy base. DermaCore is therefore not suitable for vegans or vegetarians. We are actively exploring plant-based alternatives for a future formulation. If you have specific dietary requirements, please consult a healthcare professional before use.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="dc-faq__item">
      <button class="dc-faq__question" aria-expanded="false">
        Is DermaCore safe to use during pregnancy or breastfeeding?
        <span class="dc-faq__icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      </button>
      <div class="dc-faq__answer" role="region">
        <div class="dc-faq__answer-inner">
          If you are pregnant, breastfeeding, or planning to become pregnant, we strongly recommend consulting your healthcare provider before starting any new dietary supplement — including DermaCore. While many of the individual nutrients in DermaCore are found in prenatal vitamins, the full formula has not been tested in clinical trials on pregnant or breastfeeding women, and individual needs vary. Your doctor is the best person to advise you.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="dc-faq__item">
      <button class="dc-faq__question" aria-expanded="false">
        What are the allergen and ingredient warnings?
        <span class="dc-faq__icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      </button>
      <div class="dc-faq__answer" role="region">
        <div class="dc-faq__answer-inner">
          DermaCore contains gelatin (bovine), glucose syrup, cane sugar, and natural mixed berry flavouring. It is manufactured in a facility that may also process products containing tree nuts, soy, and dairy. If you have known allergies to any ingredient, please review the full ingredient list on the label before purchasing. DermaCore is free from artificial dyes and synthetic fragrances.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

